{"tid":1943882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★調查：新年後失業者升4倍","createTime":"2020-03-26T04:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T09:11:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e33a8ea4e5783d4fa7425fdd3b0f1e46a479ae3","tid":1943882,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">農曆年後僅四分一受訪者仍全職</span><br />\n<br />\n調查發現，失業人數由農曆新年前32人，新年後至今大幅上升至161人，升幅約4倍。另外。新年前有128名受訪者擔任全職工作，新年後只剩50人仍有全職。<br />\n<br />\n至於失業原因，有三成受訪者表示因僱主或介紹人沒提供工作機會，兩成為公司裁員。團體認為，疫情嚴重打擊各行各業，基層打工仔首當其衝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/452826/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%80%85%E5%8D%874%E5%80%8D-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E4%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E7%9F%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F452826%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258D%25874%25E5%2580%258D-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%259F%25AD%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25B4%25A5%25E8%25B2%25BC&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4cls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=1836dc67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/452826/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%80%85%E5%8D%874%E5%80%8D-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E4%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E7%9F%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC</a>"},{"pid":"a5c766716c039175b815336b0e5b7d478eb49aa0","tid":1943882,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac